\pard\qc\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs32 SYSTEM IMPLEMENTATION\b0 \par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 6.0 Overview\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 This chapter presents the implementation of the Decentralized Academic Credentials Verification system. It explains how the developed system was tested, installed, and prepared for use.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 6.1 System Testing\b0 \par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 6.1.1 Unit Testing\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Unit testing was conducted on authentication, credential issuance, verification, validation, and administrative functions.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 Table 6.1: Unit Testing Summary\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Authentication | Login with valid credentials | User logged in | User logged in | Pass\par
