\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Credential issuance | Submit valid credential data | Credential issued | Credential issued | Pass\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Credential issuance | Submit incomplete data | Validation error | Validation error | Pass\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Verification | Verify valid credential | Status valid | Status valid | Pass\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Verification | Verify revoked credential | Status revoked | Status revoked | Pass\par
