\pard\qc\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs32 CHAPTER SEVEN\b0 \par
\pard\qc\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs32 CONCLUSION AND RECOMMENDATION\b0 \par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 7.0 Achievements\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 The project achieved its main objective of providing a secure and efficient platform for issuing, managing, sharing, and verifying academic credentials.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 7.1 Challenges\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Challenges included integration complexity, data consistency, user readiness, and project resource limitations.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 7.2 Proposed System Limitations\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Limitations include internet dependence, user familiarity requirements, and the need for more production hardening.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 7.3 Recommendation / Future Work\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Future work should improve integration, scalability, usability, monitoring, and institutional deployment readiness.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 7.4 Conclusion\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 The proposed system offers a practical and innovative approach to academic credential verification by improving trust, transparency, and efficiency.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 Table 7.1: Summary of Achievements, Challenges, Limitations and Recommendations\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Achievements | Secure platform for issuing, managing, sharing, and verifying academic credentials\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Challenges | Integration complexity, user readiness, and time constraints\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Limitations | Internet dependence, adoption barriers, and production-readiness considerations\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Recommendations | Improve scalability, integration, usability, and deployment readiness\par
