\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 APPENDIX A: FEASIBILITY STUDY REPORT\b0 \par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 A.1 Introduction\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 This feasibility study was conducted to determine whether the proposed Decentralized Academic Credentials Verification system is practical, sustainable, and suitable for implementation.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 A.2 Purpose of the Feasibility Study\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Determine whether the required technology and resources are available.\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Assess whether the project can be completed within the available time.\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Evaluate the expected costs and benefits.\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Determine whether intended users will be able to operate the system effectively.\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Assess whether the system can comply with legal and institutional requirements.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 A.3 Types of Feasibility Considered\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Technical Feasibility\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Economic Feasibility\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Operational Feasibility\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Legal Feasibility\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Schedule Feasibility\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 A.4 Findings of the Study\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - The proposed system is technically achievable.\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - The expected benefits justify the implementation cost.\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - Users can adopt the system with proper training.\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - The system can be implemented in compliance with legal and institutional requirements.\par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 - The project can be completed within the available time.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 A.5 Conclusion of the Feasibility Study\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Based on the findings, the proposed system is feasible and suitable for implementation.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 APPENDIX B: USER / OPERATION MANUAL\b0 \par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 B.1 Introduction\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 This manual provides guidance on how to use the Decentralized Academic Credentials Verification system.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 B.2 System Requirements\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Users require a computer or smartphone, a modern web browser, internet connectivity, and valid credentials.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 B.3 Accessing the System\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Open the system URL, click the login button, enter the required credentials, and select the appropriate role where applicable.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 B.4 Login Procedure\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Navigate to the login page, enter your email address and password, and click the login button.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 B.5 Institution Administrator Operations\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Institution administrators can issue credentials, revoke credentials, and carry out bulk imports.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 B.6 Student Operations\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Students can view, claim, share, and manage privacy settings for their credentials.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 B.7 Employer / Verifier Operations\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Employers can verify a single credential or carry out bulk verification.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 B.8 Administrator Operations\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Administrators can approve institutions and review system logs and reports.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 B.9 Troubleshooting Guide\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Check credentials, network access, input correctness, and user permissions when issues occur.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 B.10 Security Guidelines\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 Keep credentials private, log out after use, and report suspicious activity.\par
\pard\ql\sl480\slmult1 \b \f0\fs24 B.11 Conclusion\b0 \par
\pard\qj\sl480\slmult1 \f0\fs24 This manual provides the basic operational steps required to use the system effectively.\par
